            <li>Coding Spark Jobs in Scala</li>
            <li>Exploring the Spark Shell to Creating Spark Context</li>
            <li>RDD Programming</li>
            <li>Operations on RDD</li>
            <li>Transformations</li>
            <li>Actions</li>
            <li>Loading Data and Saving Data</li>
            <li>Key Value Pair RDD</li>
