            <li>Creating a Database</li>
            <li>Create a Table</li>
            <li>Inserting Data</li>
            <li>Modeling Data</li>
            <li>Creating an Application with Web</li>
            <li>Updating and Deleting Data</li>
        </pr><br>
        <h2 class="ser">Spark Integration with NoSQL (CASSANDRA) and Amazon EC2</h2>
