            <li>Introduction to Spark and Cassandra Connectors</li>
            <li>Setting Up Spark with Cassandra</li>
            <li>Creating Spark Context to Connect to Cassandra</li>
            <li>Creating Spark RDD on the Cassandra Database</li>
            <li>Performing Transformations and Actions on the Cassandra RDD</li>
            <li>Running Spark Application in Eclipse to Access Data in Cassandra</li>
            <li>Introduction to Amazon Web Services (AWS)</li>
            <li>Building a 4-Node Spark Multi-Node Cluster in AWS</li>
            <li>Deploying in Production with Mesos and YARN</li>
        </pr><br>
        <h2 class="ser">Spark Streaming</h2>
