            <li>Processing Distributed Log Files in Real Time</li>
            <li>Discretized Streams (DStreams) and RDDs</li>
            <li>Applying Transformations and Actions on Streaming Data</li>
            <li>Integration with Flume and Kafka</li>
            <li>Integration with Cassandra</li>
            <li>Monitoring Streaming Jobs</li>
        </pr><br>
        <h2 class="ser">Spark SQL</h2>
